## ðŸ“Œ **About the Plugin**
Redirect Manager is a WordPress plugin that allows users to **create, manage, and analyze URL redirects**. Unlike most redirection plugins, it **fully supports query parameters**, allowing advanced redirect handling without needing to modify `.htaccess` files.

With built-in analytics, users can track redirect hits and export reports in **CSV format**.

---

## âœ¨ **Features**
âœ… **Add, Edit, and Remove Redirects**  
âœ… **Supports Query Parameter Redirections**  
âœ… **Redirect Types:** 301, 302, 307  
âœ… **Analytics Tracking** (Hit Counts & Last Accessed Time)  
âœ… **Export Analytics Data as CSV**  
âœ… **Clear Analytics Data**  
âœ… **User-friendly Interface & Styling**  

